<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="panel ai-head">
    <view class="eyebrow">AI 潮汕旅行助手</view>
    <view class="section-title">让 AI 帮你补路线、美食和文化细节</view>
    <view class="muted">适合做 1 到 3 天路线规划、按区域找吃的、理解潮汕文化景点的看点。</view>
    <view class="cloud-tip {{cloudReady ? 'ready' : 'warning'}}">
      {{cloudReady ? '云开发已连接，AI 可通过云函数生成建议。' : '请先在 app.js 中配置云环境 ID，并部署 aiCareAssistant 云函数。'}}
    </view>
  </view>

  <scroll-view class="scene-scroll" scroll-x="true" show-scrollbar="false">
    <view class="scene-row">
      <view
        class="scene-chip {{item.active ? 'active' : ''}}"
        wx:for="{{sceneTabs}}"
        wx:key="key"
        data-scene="{{item.key}}"
        bindtap="selectScene"
      >
        {{item.label}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="panel ai-form">
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">偏好目的地</text>
      <picker range="{{destinationNames}}" value="{{destinationIndex}}" bindchange="onPickerChange">
        <view class="picker">{{destinationNames[destinationIndex]}}</view>
      </picker>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">计划天数</text>
      <input type="number" placeholder="例如 2" data-field="travelDays" bindinput="onInput" value="{{travelDays}}" />
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">描述需求</text>
      <textarea
        placeholder="{{promptPlaceholder}}"
        data-field="inputText"
        bindinput="onInput"
        value="{{inputText}}"
      ></textarea>
    </view>

    <view class="primary-btn submit-btn" bindtap="runAssistant">{{isLoading ? 'AI 正在整理中...' : '生成 AI 旅行建议'}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel ai-result" wx:if="{{result}}">
    <view class="eyebrow">AI 输出</view>
    <view class="section-title">你的潮汕建议</view>
    <view class="result-card">
      <text class="result-text">{{result}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel ai-tips" wx:if="{{!result}}">
    <view class="eyebrow">推荐场景</view>
    <view class="tip-card">
      <text class="tip-title">路线建议</text>
      <text class="muted">输入出发地、天数和偏好，AI 会给出更顺路的潮汕玩法。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tip-card">
      <text class="tip-title">美食推荐</text>
      <text class="muted">说清楚你住哪里、喜欢什么口味，AI 会按区域和时间段推荐。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tip-card">
      <text class="tip-title">文化解读</text>
      <text class="muted">适合第一次去潮州古城，先理解景点意义再去会更有沉浸感。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

